{"id": "1404", "post": "<div class=\"post-1404 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-amazon-com tag-xen\" id=\"post-1404\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/amazon-free-ec2-micro-instance-613mb-xen-vps-for-1-year/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Amazon \u2013 FREE EC2 Micro Instance (613MB Xen VPS) for 1 Year</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/amazon-com/\" rel=\"tag\">amazon.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> October 22, 2010 @ 1:16 am, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://aws.amazon.com/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/images/amazonaws.jpg\" class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"Amazon AWS\"></a> Via <a href=\"http://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=1816773\">Hacker News</a>. <a href=\"http://aws.amazon.com/\"><b>Amazon Web Services</b></a> apparently just released a <a href=\"http://aws.amazon.com/free/\">Free Tier</a> which includes quite a few nice freebies <em>for whole year</em>, including a <b>free</b> 750 hours/month <a href=\"http://aws.amazon.com/ue2/\">Amazone EC2</a> Micro Instance (i.e. enough to run for the whole month). It comes with:</p><ul><li>613MB memory</li><li>10GB storage (via Amazon Elastic Block Storage) with limit of 1 million I/Os.</li><li>30GB/month data transfer</li><li>Xen \u2014 32 bit or 64 bit</li></ul><p>Not to mention 5GB of Amazon S3 storage for backups. 1GB of SimpleDB storage, and other free quota for other Amazon Web Services. Did I mention <b>FREE</b>?! No better time for the entrepreneurs amongst us to get started on the next arse-kicking web app (or evil world domination plan, if it is your thing, Bwahahahah!!!) Micro instance is available in either North Virginia, California, Ireland and Singapore.</p><p>Another sure thing is \u2014 it is not likely you\u2019ll see Amazon.com in <a href=\"/category/deadpool/\">Dead Pool</a> within a year. So your FREE VPS are in safe hands!</p><p>Now the catch \u2014 (1) this is for new customers only. Or maybe you just need a new email address to sign up. (2) a credit card is needed for signing up. Yeah I guess you can\u2019t execute your evil world domination plan without a credit card either.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Famazon-free-ec2-micro-instance-613mb-xen-vps-for-1-year%2F&amp;t=Amazon%20-%20FREE%20EC2%20Micro%20Instance%20%28613MB%20Xen%20VPS%29%20for%201%20Year\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Amazon%20-%20FREE%20EC2%20Micro%20Instance%20%28613MB%20Xen%20VPS%29%20for%201%20Year&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Famazon-free-ec2-micro-instance-613mb-xen-vps-for-1-year%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\